title: Genesis - Live in Zurich 1977 (m4a)
description:
Soundboard recording of Genesis live in Zurich, Switzerland during their Wind and Wuthering tour in 1977:

DISC 1:
Squonk
One For The Vine
Robbery, Assault & Battery
Inside And Out
Firth Of Fifth
The Carpet Crawlers
...In That Quiet Earth
Afterglow
I Know What I Like (In Your Wardrobe)

DISC 2:
Eleventh Earl Of Mar
Supper's Ready
Dance On A Volcano
Drum Duet
Los Endos
The Lamb Lies Down On Broadway
The Musical Box (Closing Section)

Enjoy!

Lineup:
Phil Collins - vocals, drums and percussion
Steve Hackett - guitars
Michael Rutherford - bass, guitars, bass pedals
Tony Banks - keyboards
Chester Thompson - drums and percussion
